article.headline: N.C. State whomps Arkansas State 80-59
article.story:
LAS VEGAS (AP) -- Billie McDowell had 17 points and nine assists
to help North Carolina State (unranked ESPN/USA Today; No. 23 AP) beat Arkansas State 80-59 on
Sunday in the Gray Division third-place game in the Duel in the
Desert tournament.

Khadijan Whittington had 19 rebounds and 13 points, and Gillian
Goring and Tiffany Stansbury had 14 points each for the Wolfpack
(7-3).

Adrianne Davie led the Lady Indians (5-5) with 18 points and 10
rebounds.
